title: Some resolutions on creating SkillDAO
body:
1. Increase promotion and publicity to attract more users to participate in Dao governance
2. Communicate with more Dao organizations to improve the ecological environment of SkillDAO
3. Add item filtering and sorting
4. Attract funds to invest in SkillDAO
